# ─── Deriv API Credentials ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VITE_APP_ID   : Your Deriv App ID (required)
#                 Default 67985 works for testing. Get yours at https://api.deriv.com/
#
# VITE_CLIENT_ID: Your OAuth2 Client ID (required for PKCE / new auth flow)
#                 Get yours at https://developers.binary.com/ or Deriv API dashboard
#                 If blank → falls back to legacy token redirect (acct1/token1/cur1)
#
# Auth flow detection (automatic):
#   VITE_CLIENT_ID set   → OAuth2 PKCE flow  (login + sign-up, ?code= callback)
#   VITE_CLIENT_ID empty → Legacy token flow  (login only,    ?acct1= callback)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_APP_ID=
VITE_CLIENT_ID=
